game.name: Sebastian Cupcakes
game.description:
One of the best kitchen games to play for girls, Sebastian Cupcakes has everything you need to make your cooking adventure interesting. In this brand new game, we are going to share with you a wonderful cupcake recipe that you have not tried yet. It is really hard to find out the delicious cupcakes, but you are lucky one who will get a chance to prepare it together. Hope you all will have fun in this free online cooking game for girls! The process is quite simple, but only requires to follow the needful instructions. 

This cool kitchen game is just for you if you are a true lover of Little Mermaid. The story of this game will be surrounded by the cutest and gorgeous mermaid and her beloved hum prince. Sebastian is one of the adorable and most important characters in the story. You will have to prepare some scrumptious cupcakes in the honour of Sebastian. Begin this cool kitchen game with preparing the batter first. For this, mix baking powder, flower, milk, vanilla extract, eggs, sugar and butter into a bowl.

Collect the paper cups and pour the batter in them. Now place them in a special tray. Take an oven and bake the muffins into it until they turn into a golden color. Mix blue food coloring, milk, powder sugar and butter for the icing. Check if your new cream gets cool down and use it to frost the cupcakes. You can use an oval red marzipan to create the arms, mouth and head of Sebastian. To create her eyes, go with white fondant and black confetti. All the best to have a blast in this latest cooking game for children!
